Conclusion: 
This project has really helped me get a stronger understanding of the vectors, it was difficult at first but after putting more time aside to understand them I have realized why they are so important for this project. While there are many ways that you can complete this project I feel that the way that I decided was a very effective one. Separating the functions allowed me to focus on just one problem at a time and understand when and why something was not working. Overall, this project taught me things about C++ that I didn’t know, and allowed me to build upon the things I was familiar with. 



